{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.1","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:1","prev_osis_id":"Jer.004.031,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.005.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">La mesure du p\u00e9ch\u00e9 d\u2019Isra\u00ebl et de Juda est comble<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-9: cf. Os 4:1-7. So 3:1-8.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Jer.5.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Parcourez les rues de J\u00e9rusalem,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Regardez, informez-vous, cherchez dans les places,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">S\u2019il s\u2019y trouve un homme, s\u2019il y en a un<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Qui pratique la justice, qui s\u2019attache \u00e0 la v\u00e9rit\u00e9,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et je pardonne \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.5","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.5.2","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:2","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.4.31","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 4:31","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.4.31"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.2","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:2","prev_osis_id":"Jer.005.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.005.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Jer.5.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>M\u00eame quand ils disent: L\u2019\u00c9ternel est vivant!<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">C\u2019est faussement qu\u2019ils jurent.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.5","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.5.3","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:3","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.5.1","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:1","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.3","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:3","prev_osis_id":"Jer.005.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.005.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Jer.5.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>\u00c9ternel, tes yeux n\u2019aper\u00e7oivent-ils pas la v\u00e9rit\u00e9?<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Tu les frappes, et ils ne sentent rien;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Tu les consumes, et ils ne veulent pas recevoir instruction;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Ils prennent un visage plus dur que le roc,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Ils refusent de se convertir.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.5","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.5.4","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:4","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.5.2","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:2","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.4","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:4","prev_osis_id":"Jer.005.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.005.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Jer.5.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Je disais: Ce ne sont que les petits;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Ils agissent en insens\u00e9s, parce qu\u2019ils ne connaissent pas la voie de l\u2019\u00c9ternel,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">La loi de leur Dieu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.5","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.5.5","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:5","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.5.3","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:3","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.5","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:5","prev_osis_id":"Jer.005.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.005.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Jer.5.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>J\u2019irai vers les grands, et je leur parlerai;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Car eux, ils connaissent la voie de l\u2019\u00c9ternel,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">La loi de leur Dieu;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Mais ils ont tous aussi bris\u00e9 le joug,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Rompu les liens.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.5","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.5.6","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:6","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.5.4","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:4","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.6","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:6","prev_osis_id":"Jer.005.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.005.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Jer.5.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>C\u2019est pourquoi le lion de la for\u00eat les tue,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Le loup du d\u00e9sert les d\u00e9truit,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">La panth\u00e8re est aux aguets devant leurs villes;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Tous ceux qui en sortiront seront d\u00e9chir\u00e9s;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Car leurs transgressions sont nombreuses,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Leurs infid\u00e9lit\u00e9s se sont multipli\u00e9es.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.5","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.5.7","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:7","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.5.5","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:5","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.7","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:7","prev_osis_id":"Jer.005.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.005.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Jer.5.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Pourquoi te pardonnerais-je?<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Tes enfants m\u2019ont abandonn\u00e9,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et ils jurent par des dieux qui n\u2019existent pas.<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">J\u2019ai re\u00e7u leurs serments, et ils se livrent \u00e0 l\u2019adult\u00e8re,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Ils sont en foule dans la maison de la prostitu\u00e9e.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.5","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.5.8","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:8","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.5.6","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:6","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.8","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:8","prev_osis_id":"Jer.005.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.005.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Jer.5.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Semblables \u00e0 des chevaux bien nourris, qui courent \u00e7\u00e0 et l\u00e0,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">\n    Ils hennissent chacun apr\u00e8s la femme de son prochain.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.5","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.5.9","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:9","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.5.7","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:7","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.9","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:9","prev_osis_id":"Jer.005.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.005.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Jer.5.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>\n    Ne ch\u00e2tierais-je pas ces choses-l\u00e0, dit l\u2019\u00c9ternel,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Ne me vengerais-je pas d\u2019une pareille nation?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.5","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.5.10","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:10","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.5.8","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:8","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.10","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:10","prev_osis_id":"Jer.005.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.005.011,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 10-19: cf. J\u00e9 6:1-15. De 28:30-33.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Jer.5.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Montez sur ses murailles, et abattez,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Mais ne d\u00e9truisez pas enti\u00e8rement!<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Enlevez ses ceps<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Qui n\u2019appartiennent point \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.5","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.5.11","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:11","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.5.9","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:9","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.11","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:11","prev_osis_id":"Jer.005.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.005.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Jer.5.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Car la maison d\u2019Isra\u00ebl et la maison de Juda m\u2019ont \u00e9t\u00e9 infid\u00e8les,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Dit l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.5","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.5.12","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:12","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.5.10","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:10","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.12","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:12","prev_osis_id":"Jer.005.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.005.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Jer.5.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Ils renient l\u2019\u00c9ternel, ils disent: Il n\u2019existe pas!<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">\n    Et le malheur ne viendra pas sur nous,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Nous ne verrons ni l\u2019\u00e9p\u00e9e ni la famine.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.5","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.5.13","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:13","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.5.11","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:11","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.13","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:13","prev_osis_id":"Jer.005.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.005.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Jer.5.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Les proph\u00e8tes ne sont que du vent,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et personne ne parle en eux.<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Qu\u2019il leur soit fait ainsi!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.5","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.5.14","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:14","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.5.12","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:12","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.14","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:14","prev_osis_id":"Jer.005.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.005.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Jer.5.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>C\u2019est pourquoi ainsi parle l\u2019\u00c9ternel, le Dieu des arm\u00e9es:<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Parce que vous avez dit cela,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Voici, je veux que ma parole dans ta bouche soit du feu,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et ce peuple du bois, et que ce feu les consume.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.5","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.5.15","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:15","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.5.13","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:13","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.15","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:15","prev_osis_id":"Jer.005.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.005.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Jer.5.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Voici, je fais venir de loin une nation contre vous, maison d\u2019Isra\u00ebl,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Dit l\u2019\u00c9ternel;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">C\u2019est une nation forte, c\u2019est une nation ancienne,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Une nation dont tu ne connais pas la langue,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et dont tu ne comprendras point les paroles.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.5","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.5.16","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:16","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.5.14","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:14","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.16","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:16","prev_osis_id":"Jer.005.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.005.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Jer.5.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Son carquois est comme un s\u00e9pulcre ouvert;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Ils sont tous des h\u00e9ros.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.5","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.5.17","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:17","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.5.15","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:15","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.17","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:17","prev_osis_id":"Jer.005.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.005.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Jer.5.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Elle d\u00e9vorera ta moisson et ton pain,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Elle d\u00e9vorera tes fils et tes filles,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Elle d\u00e9vorera tes brebis et tes b\u0153ufs,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Elle d\u00e9vorera ta vigne et ton figuier;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Elle d\u00e9truira par l\u2019\u00e9p\u00e9e tes villes fortes dans lesquelles tu te confies.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.5","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.5.18","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:18","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.5.16","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:16","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.18","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:18","prev_osis_id":"Jer.005.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.005.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Jer.5.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Mais en ces jours, dit l\u2019\u00c9ternel,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Je ne vous d\u00e9truirai pas enti\u00e8rement.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.5","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.5.19","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:19","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.5.17","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:17","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.19","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:19","prev_osis_id":"Jer.005.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.005.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Jer.5.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>Si vous dites alors:<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">\n    Pourquoi l\u2019\u00c9ternel, notre Dieu, nous fait-il tout cela?<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Tu leur r\u00e9pondras: Comme vous m\u2019avez abandonn\u00e9,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et que vous avez servi des dieux \u00e9trangers dans votre pays,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Ainsi vous servirez des \u00e9trangers dans un pays qui n\u2019est pas le v\u00f4tre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.5","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.5.20","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:20","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.5.18","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:18","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.20","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:20","prev_osis_id":"Jer.005.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.005.021,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 20-31: cf. (Job 37:23, 24; 38:8-11. Pr 1:7, 29-32.) (Mi 6:9-12. So 3:1-4.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Jer.5.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>Annoncez ceci \u00e0 la maison de Jacob,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Publiez-le en Juda, et dites:<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.5","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.5.21","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:21","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.5.19","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:19","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.21","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:21","prev_osis_id":"Jer.005.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.005.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Jer.5.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>\n    \u00c9coutez ceci, peuple insens\u00e9, et qui n\u2019as point de c\u0153ur!<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Ils ont des yeux et ne voient point,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Ils ont des oreilles et n\u2019entendent point.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.5","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.5.22","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:22","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.5.20","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:20","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.22","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:22","prev_osis_id":"Jer.005.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.005.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Jer.5.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Ne me craindrez-vous pas, dit l\u2019\u00c9ternel,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Ne tremblerez-vous pas devant moi?<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">C\u2019est moi qui ai donn\u00e9 \u00e0 la mer le sable pour limite,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Limite \u00e9ternelle qu\u2019elle ne doit pas franchir;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Ses flots s\u2019agitent, mais ils sont impuissants;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Ils mugissent, mais ils ne la franchissent pas.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.5","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.5.23","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:23","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.5.21","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:21","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.23","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:23","prev_osis_id":"Jer.005.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.005.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Jer.5.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>Ce peuple a un c\u0153ur indocile et rebelle;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Ils se r\u00e9voltent, et s\u2019en vont.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.5","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.5.24","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:24","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.5.22","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:22","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.24","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:24","prev_osis_id":"Jer.005.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.005.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Jer.5.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>Ils ne disent pas dans leur c\u0153ur:<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Craignons l\u2019\u00c9ternel, notre Dieu,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Qui donne la pluie en son temps,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">\n    La pluie de la premi\u00e8re et de l\u2019arri\u00e8re saison,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et qui nous r\u00e9serve les semaines destin\u00e9es \u00e0 la moisson.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.5","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.5.25","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:25","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.5.23","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:23","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.25","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:25","prev_osis_id":"Jer.005.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.005.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Jer.5.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>C\u2019est \u00e0 cause de vos iniquit\u00e9s que ces dispensations n\u2019ont pas lieu,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Ce sont vos p\u00e9ch\u00e9s qui vous privent de ces biens.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.5","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.5.26","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:26","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.5.24","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:24","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.26","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:26","prev_osis_id":"Jer.005.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.005.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Jer.5.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>Car il se trouve parmi mon peuple des m\u00e9chants;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Ils \u00e9pient comme l\u2019oiseleur qui dresse des pi\u00e8ges,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Ils tendent des filets, et prennent des hommes.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.5","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.5.27","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:27","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.5.25","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:25","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.27","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:27","prev_osis_id":"Jer.005.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.005.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Jer.5.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>Comme une cage est remplie d\u2019oiseaux,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Leurs maisons sont remplies de fraude;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">C\u2019est ainsi qu\u2019ils deviennent puissants et riches.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.5","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.5.28","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:28","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.5.26","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:26","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.28","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:28","prev_osis_id":"Jer.005.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.005.029,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Jer.5.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup>\n    Ils s\u2019engraissent, ils sont brillants d\u2019embonpoint;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Ils d\u00e9passent toute mesure dans le mal,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">\n    Ils ne d\u00e9fendent pas la cause, la cause de l\u2019orphelin, et ils prosp\u00e8rent;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Ils ne font pas droit aux indigents.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.5","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.5.29","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:29","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.29"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.5.27","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:27","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"29","lastverse":"29","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.29","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.29","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:29","prev_osis_id":"Jer.005.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.005.030,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Jer.5.29\" class=\"v\">29<\/sup>\n    Ne ch\u00e2tierais-je pas ces choses-l\u00e0, dit l\u2019\u00c9ternel,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Ne me vengerais-je pas d\u2019une pareille nation?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.5","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.5.30","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:30","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.30"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.5.28","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:28","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"30","lastverse":"30","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.30","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.30","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:30","prev_osis_id":"Jer.005.029,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.005.031,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Jer.5.30\" class=\"v\">30<\/sup>Des choses horribles, abominables,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Se font dans le pays.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.5","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.5.31","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:31","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.31"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.5.29","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:29","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.29"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"31","lastverse":"31","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.31","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.31","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:31","prev_osis_id":"Jer.005.030,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.006.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Jer.5.31\" class=\"v\">31<\/sup>Les proph\u00e8tes proph\u00e9tisent avec fausset\u00e9,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Les sacrificateurs dominent sous leur conduite,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et mon peuple prend plaisir \u00e0 cela.<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Que ferez-vous \u00e0 la fin?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.5","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.6.1","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 6:1","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.6.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.5.30","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 5:30","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.5.30"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fc3bce859.29287164');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fc3bce859.29287164\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fc3bce859.29287164","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fc3bce859.29287164'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fc3bce859.29287164\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}